dct_title_s: Mapa de la Ciudad de Salta : calles - alturas, aveniads - plazas, referencias turísticas, accesos / cartografia Guillermo Cimarelli.
dct_description_sm: Shows roads, traffic flow circulation shown by red arrows, public buildings , places of worship, cemeteries, and tourists sites. Some relief shown by shading. Bottom of cover panel: Latinbaires Editores S.R.L. Top of cover panel: 29. Ancillary Maps: "Accesos a Salta" , "Alrededores de Salta" , "Detalle Centro" , "Detalle continuacion". Includes: index to streets, and location maps.
